{"tid":1298083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂］致所有義士 請集中火力 幫手推返重點post","createTime":"2019-07-08T18:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T19:04:52.000Z","uid":175770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cde6c9c190b8c917e333ff095cbaf3e59334a698","tid":1298083,"uid":175770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"社運尚未完結 我諗好多人會開始鬆懈 甚至玩膠 今晚既事我相信大家都好清楚 （我有份留言第一個外語post 先係到講聲對唔住）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先</span> 希望大家集中火力 唔好因為玩膠玩出禍 香港仲需要你地！唔好忘記逝去既生命 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地既訴求 一個都未達到 切勿鬆懈！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 今晚出左 返黎上連登好撚嬲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297715</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好灰心！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後</span> 呼籲大家推返有用既post 上熱門  俾更多人睇到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 我地有好多義士等緊我地去幫</span><br />\n<br />\n急！！！  我有個 旺角義士朋友 需要大家幫幫手拯救！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295823</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後</span> 聽日屯門要人 幫手推埋<br />\n<br />\n【突發】聽朝9點 屯門區議會 要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297048</a><br />\n<br />\n其他post 都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請集中火力 一齊share"},{"pid":"95d14044c71857d3d72564bac204a5ff5744de9d","tid":1298083,"uid":175770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:32:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2247c8be730c0c63db7de39f4cb07aafa7d76dd4","tid":1298083,"uid":42852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">幫手